Quarter: The quarter of the year for which the employee turnover rate is being reported.
Year: The year for which the employee turnover rate is being reported.
Employee Turnover Rate: The percentage of employees who left the company during the quarter.
Total Employees: The total number of employees at the company during the quarter.
New Hires: The number of new employees hired during the quarter.
Departures: The number of employees who left the company during the quarter.
